CREATE VIEW `plantactivesummary` AS select `p`.`plantId` AS `plantId`,`p`.`plantTag` AS `plantTag`,`p`.`plantName` AS `plantName`,`p`.`acquisitionDate` AS `acquisitionDate`,`p`.`acquisitionSource` AS `acquisitionSource`,`g`.`genusName` AS `genusName`,`s`.`speciesName` AS `speciesName`,`s`.`hybridName` AS `hybridName`,`pcl`.`locationName` AS `locationName`,`pcl`.`locationTypeCode` AS `locationTypeCode`,`pcl`.`locationStartDateTime` AS `locationStartDateTime` from (((`plant` `p` left join `taxon` `s` on((`s`.`taxonId` = `p`.`taxonId`))) left join `genus` `g` on((`g`.`genusId` = `s`.`genusId`))) left join `plantcurrentlocation` `pcl` on((`pcl`.`plantId` = `p`.`plantId`))) where (`p`.`isActive` = 1);

